videoDetails.Title: The Most Insane Medium Tank
videoDetails.Description:
Decal affiliate link: https://tinyurl.com/42thwzv3

The Swedish Strv m/42 DT or Delat Torn is probably my all-time favorite medium tank in War Thunder. With potent APHE rounds and a rapid 3.0s reload rate, it makes for the perfect ambush vehicle. It is also fairly versatile, though the armor is not good at all.  Gaijin did nerf its replenishment since the last update, however.

Check the channel "About" section for the link to the creator of my profile picture.

Command and Conquer: Generals - Makin' A Sweep, Fight For Peace, In The Field, Comanche Down
